It's my profession after all...", 'But seeing others injured or even lose their lives still hurts me...', "S-sorry, I don't mean to... Um... W-would you mind... patting me on the head instead?"]

['Yesterday I found a new medical book in the database!', 'It claimed that there are many ways to treat wounds without resorting to drugs or machinery...', 'One of which includes the usage of affirmative body contact techniques...', 'Such as patting someone on the head to praise or comfort them.']
['Ah! Commandant, what are you...? T-that makes me all giddy inside somehow.']
